Permanent Fix — Change MySQL port in docker-compose.yml
Open docker/docker-compose.yml → find mysql ports → change:
yaml
    ports:
      - "3306:3306"
To:
yaml
    ports:
      - "3307:3306"
This way Docker MySQL uses port 3307 and your local MySQL keeps 3306 — no conflict ever again! ✅
Then:
powershell
docker-compose down
docker-compose up -d
