## Why This Keeps Happening?
```
Your laptop has MySQL installed locally → uses port 3306
Docker MySQL also wants port 3306
= Two things fighting for same port ❌

Solution:
Local MySQL  → 3306 (unchanged)
Docker MySQL → 3307 (different port)
= No conflict ever! ✅


